data.description: Introducing this charming corner lot home with a side entry garage! Situated on a spacious lot, this property offers plenty of room to spread out and enjoy outdoor activities. As you step onto the front porch, you'll notice a delightful swing, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the fresh air. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a large great room, providing ample space for entertaining family and friends. The great room flows into the dining area, creating an open and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring a breakfast bar and a bay window breakfast nook. Retreat to the large master suite, which offers a peaceful sanctuary with a soaking tub and a separate shower. The additional bedrooms are spacious and offer plenty of room. Located on a corner lot, this home offers privacy and convenience. Just a short walk or bike ride to Mary Lee Clark​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ Elementary.
